Maintainer: Denisson Silva <denissoncsol@gmail.com>     
Description: The ceapBR package provides tools to retrieve and clean data from the Quota for the Exercise of Parliamentary Activity (CEAP) in Brazil. 
  It currently supports data collection from the Chamber of Deputies and the Federal Senate.
